          "tz": -420
        },
        "subject": "LU-11819 tests: combine similar functionality in lib",
        "message": "LU-11819 tests: combine similar functionality in lib\n\nThere are several Lustre test scripts that run tests from an\nexternal program. These executables are themselves composed of\nseveral test routines. We should pull out all the common routines,\nstructures, etc. from each of these test (.c) programs and create\na library that they can link to.\n\nThis work will cut down on code duplication.\n\nTo start this effort, pull out common functionality and structures\nfrom llapi_layout_tests.c and mmap_sanity.c and put them into\nlibtestutils.c .\n\nTest-Parameters: trivial envdefinitions=ONLY=27D testlist=sanity\nTest-Parameters: envdefinitions=ONLY=18 testlist=sanityn\nSigned-off-by: James Nunez <jnunez@whamcloud.com>\nChange-Id: I3c892b0e6f1d4891655992fbd871b790bf2a3922\n"
      },
      "branch": "refs/heads/master"
    }
  },
